频；以色列国防军：我们的心与她的家人同在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/hamas-publishes-video-of-israeli-soldier-held-hostage-idf-our-heart-is-with-her-family/0000018b-caba-dd30-a5ff-effb39210000</link><description>10 月 7 日，19 岁的诺亚·马西亚诺 (Noa Marciano) 在纳哈尔奥兹基布兹 (Kibbutz Nahal Oz) 的以色列国防军观察基地被抓走</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 22:25:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/hamas-publishes-video-of-israeli-soldier-held-hostage-idf-our-heart-is-with-her-family/0000018b-caba-dd30-a5ff-effb39210000</guid></item><item><title>伊拉克亲民兵组织 Telegram 频道发布人质视频，显示在伊拉克失踪的以色列学者伊丽莎白·楚尔科夫 (Elizabeth Tsurkov)</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/iraqi-telegram-channels-publish-video-of-israeli-hostage-elizabeth-tsurkov/0000018b-ca84-dd30-a5ff-efe53e170000</link><description>37 岁的楚尔科夫被拍摄到她呼吁结束加沙战斗，并要求采取行动释放她。楚尔科夫拥有以色列和俄罗斯双重国籍，自三月以来一直被伊拉克什叶派武装组织卡塔伊布真主党关押。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 21:37:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/iraqi-telegram-channels-publish-video-of-israeli-hostage-elizabeth-tsurkov/0000018b-ca84-dd30-a5ff-efe53e170000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长要求将所有机密材料违反程序发送至总理办公室</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-attorney-general-demands-to-see-all-classified-material-sent-to-pms-office/0000018b-ca64-d8c7-a59b-df6d43550000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的幕僚长试图违反政府规定收集国家安全机密文件，此举显然是为了避免因 10 月 7 日的灾难而受到指责</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 21:24:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-attorney-general-demands-to-see-all-classified-material-sent-to-pms-office/0000018b-ca64-d8c7-a59b-df6d43550000</guid></item><item><title>外交部长埃利·科恩估计，以色列还有两到三周的时间才能加大国际压力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/fm-cohen-israel-has-between-two-and-three-weeks-before-international-pressure-intensifies/0000018b-ca38-df9a-ab8b-def8d8c00000</link><description>以色列外交部长伊莱·科恩承认国际社会对加沙战斗暂停的压力越来越大，他表示“10月7日大屠杀的震惊已经减轻”，并且“最近几天，世界媒体主要展示来自加沙的图像”</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 20:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/fm-cohen-israel-has-between-two-and-three-weeks-before-international-pressure-intensifies/0000018b-ca38-df9a-ab8b-def8d8c00000</guid></item><item><title>《沉默之声》的讽刺成为以色列生活的完美隐喻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-13/ty-article/.highlight/satirical-take-on-the-sound-of-silence-becomes-perfect-metaphor-for-life-in-israel/0000018b-c9e1-df9a-ab8b-dfe9bac40000</link><description>《离开这里》是一首 10 月 7 日之后的以色列歌曲，以 60 年代经典音乐为背景，立即成为反政府热门歌曲。但这首歌并不是对忧郁情绪的不敬的转折；只是阴郁</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 20:18:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-13/ty-article/.highlight/satirical-take-on-the-sound-of-silence-becomes-perfect-metaphor-for-life-in-israel/0000018b-c9e1-df9a-ab8b-dfe9bac40000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫医院发言人在解救哈马斯人质后举行有争议的新闻发布会，被传唤参加解散前听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-hospital-spokesperson-summoned-after-freed-hostages-presser/0000018b-c9fb-df9a-ab8b-dffb47b50000</link><description>在伊奇洛夫医院工作了 14 年的阿维·肖山 (Avi Shoshan) 因协助召开新闻发布会而被强制休假，约切韦德·利夫什茨 (Yocheved Lifshitz) 表示，哈马斯对她“非常友好”</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 19:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-hospital-spokesperson-summoned-after-freed-hostages-presser/0000018b-c9fb-df9a-ab8b-dffb47b50000</guid></item><item><title>与以色列其他地区相比，贝都因学校拥有防空洞的可能性要小得多</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-schools-are-much-less-likely-to-have-bomb-shelters-compared-to-rest-of-israel/0000018b-c9a5-df9a-ab8b-dfed716a0000</link><description>随着以色列在加沙与哈马斯交战，附近内盖夫数以万计的贝都因儿童就读于缺乏避难所或避难所不符合民防标准的学校</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 19:08:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-schools-are-much-less-likely-to-have-bomb-shelters-compared-to-rest-of-israel/0000018b-c9a5-df9a-ab8b-dfed716a0000</guid></item><item><title>随着加沙战争的进行，以色列定居者袭击巴勒斯坦人，并在约旦河西岸创造了新的现实</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-attack-palestinians-and-create-a-new-reality-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-c965-dd8b-abbf-dfff567c0000</link><description>当以色列国防军和辛贝特在加沙地带忙碌时，约旦河西岸定居者却利用战争入侵私人土地、攻击巴勒斯坦人并用军事武器武装自己</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 18:43:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-attack-palestinians-and-create-a-new-reality-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-c965-dd8b-abbf-dfff567c0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么我的左翼非政府组织这次不支持与哈马斯停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-my-leftist-ngo-wont-back-a-cease-fire-with-hamas-this-time/0000018b-c95d-d353-a3fb-cffd1e020000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 18:27:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-my-leftist-ngo-wont-back-a-cease-fire-with-hamas-this-time/0000018b-c95d-d353-a3fb-cffd1e020000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的犹太巨额捐助者正在犯一个灾难性的错误</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/trumps-jewish-megadonors-are-making-a-disastrous-mistake/0000018b-c953-dd8b-abbf-dfffcb600000</link><description>在反犹太主义在美国爆发、以色列面临生存威胁之际，特朗普的犹太辩护者为什么会支持一个容易受到共和党孤立主义抬头的普京谄媚者、一个对以色列没有真正信念的、煽动犹太人的活生生的引擎呢？</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 18:08:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.p